text:
Good sugarcane juice. Decent cup size and not too diluted (ie. the drink is a dark shade of green, not yellowish). Friendly service by the  aunty who prepped the drink too!

Note: the photo shows my beverage partially consumed. The cup was FULL when served. I was just very thirsty. LOL!
Tried their ice black tea. Probably one of the worst Iâ€™ve tried. Took a sip and threw both away. Too stale and strong. Indian drinks stalls down that stretch makes way better ice tea.
This place opens at 2.30pm at least on Thursday
